bdf2sfd 1.1.8 release.
Update ChangeLog.
Harmonize the line on packages availability across all projects.
Move manual page to the man directory.

Add missing void to the usage() function definition.

Fixes -Wstrict-prototype warning issued by Clang 15.
Bump copyright year to 2023.
Point the OpenBSD package link to openports.pl.
Add a link to the FreeBSD package in the README.
Remove unneeded <sys/types.h> include.
Bump copyright year to 2022.
bdf2sfd 1.1.7 release.
Update ChangeLog.

Switch to using getline(3) instead of fgets(3).

This allows reading lines of arbitrary length, and performance testing
using hyperfine didn't show any significant regressions.
Use CMAKE_C_STANDARD instead of hardcoding compiler flags.
